l:dependency.name: Test Odyssey Plugin for Jenkins
l:dependency.l:description: Test Odyssey is a scriptless cloud based testing tool. This plugin enables users to trigger execution runs on Test Odyssey from Continuous Integration or Continuous Delivery setup on Jenkins.

l:dependency.name: Apache Commons Validator
l:dependency.l:description: Apache Commons Validator provides the building blocks for both client side validation and server side data validation. It may be used standalone or with a framework like Struts.

l:dependency.name: Jackson
l:dependency.l:description: Jackson is a high-performance JSON processor (parser, generator)

l:dependency.name: Apache Commons BeanUtils
l:dependency.l:description: Apache Commons BeanUtils provides an easy-to-use but flexible wrapper around reflection and introspection.

l:dependency.name: Data Mapper for Jackson
l:dependency.l:description: Data Mapper package is a high-performance data binding package built on Jackson JSON processor

l:dependency.name: Apache Commons Codec
l:dependency.l:description: The Apache Commons Codec package contains simple encoder and decoders for various formats such as Base64 and Hexadecimal. In addition to these widely used encoders and decoders, the codec package also maintains a collection of phonetic encoding utilities.

l:dependency.name: Commons Digester
l:dependency.l:description: The Digester package lets you configure an XML to Java object mapping module which triggers certain actions called rules whenever a particular pattern of nested XML elements is recognized.

l:dependency.name: Apache Commons Collections
l:dependency.l:description: Types that extend and augment the Java Collections Framework.
